    <item>
      <title>如果弗里兰当选，她将取消加拿大资本利得税上调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/chrystia-freeland-to-scrap-canada-capital-gains-hike-if-she-s-elected-as-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，如果克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰 (Chrystia Freeland) 赢得取代贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 担任总理的竞选，她将放弃加拿大政府提高资本利得纳入税率的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/chrystia-freeland-to-scrap-canada-capital-gains-hike-if-she-s-elected-as-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 18:59:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱在达沃斯称赞特朗普，但寻求与中国建立更深层次的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/milei-s-davos-outing-twins-trump-praise-with-pragmatism-on-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 上台仅仅一年多后，就获得了大选的授权，他将撕毁规则，采取一切必要措施扭转阿根廷的局面，现在，他觉得自己的撕毁规则的执政方式得到了证明。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/milei-s-davos-outing-twins-trump-praise-with-pragmatism-on-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 18:08:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克和奥特曼就特朗普大肆宣传的 100 亿美元人工智能项目发生争执</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/musk-says-firms-backing-trump-ai-initiative-don-t-have-the-money</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克公开质疑那些加入唐纳德·特朗普总统承诺投资数千亿美元用于人工智能基础设施建设的公司是否能够兑现承诺，这暴露了白宫内部早期的裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/musk-says-firms-backing-trump-ai-initiative-don-t-have-the-money</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 17:50:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼将向墨西哥边境派遣多达 1,500 名现役军人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-22/urgent-pentagon-to-send-up-to-1-500-active-duty-troops-to-help-secure-us-mexico-border-officials-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿（美联社）——美国官员周三表示，五角大楼将在未来几天开始部署多达 1,500 名现役军人，帮助确保南部边境的安全，以实施唐纳德·特朗普总统上任后不久在行政命令中提出的打击移民计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-22/urgent-pentagon-to-send-up-to-1-500-active-duty-troops-to-help-secure-us-mexico-border-officials-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 17:34:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求普京就乌克兰问题“达成协议”，否则将承担代价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-tells-putin-to-make-a-deal-on-ukraine-or-face-new-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普加大对俄罗斯的压力，要求其通过谈判结束乌克兰战争，并威胁说，如果俄罗斯拒绝迅速结束战争，将对俄罗斯实施经济处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-tells-putin-to-make-a-deal-on-ukraine-or-face-new-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 16:51:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>吸食可卡因的私人军队引发哥伦比亚难民危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/venezuelan-jets-buzz-border-as-colombians-flee-guerrilla-terror</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数以万计的难民逃离哥伦比亚最大的可卡因生产区之一，以躲避自 2016 年和平协议以来最严重的暴力事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/venezuelan-jets-buzz-border-as-colombians-flee-guerrilla-terror</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 16:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普允许在学校和教堂逮捕移民后，各大城市做好迎接突袭的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-offers-immigration-agents-new-freedoms-for-arrests-amid-broad-changes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统誓言开始大规模驱逐出境并发布命令包括授权移民局进入教堂和学校等先前受到保护的场所后，从纽约到芝加哥和洛杉矶等城市的移民社区仍然处于紧张状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-offers-immigration-agents-new-freedoms-for-arrests-amid-broad-changes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 23:16:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银与 OpenAI、甲骨文签署特朗普公布的 AI 协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-to-announce-joint-openai-softbank-oracle-ai-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软银集团公司、OpenAI 和甲骨文公司正在组建一家价值 1000 亿美元的合资企业，为人工智能基础设施提供资金，这是与唐纳德·特朗普总统共同宣布的一项举措，旨在加速新兴技术的发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-to-announce-joint-openai-softbank-oracle-ai-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 18:13:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
